GeneRangeExtractor - Class in engine
Extract Gene mentions in a given text Implements the RangeExtractor interface and extract gene sequence in a input text using HMM GENETAG and Genia TokenShapeChunker from LingPipe This use a slightly extended singleton design pattern that stores a set of "singletons" in a Map that can be used to retrieve a "singletons" of different models, to make sure each unique model is only loaded once
